=== 虛擬犯罪 ===
海盜、收取保護費與偷竊皆是遊戲內容之一，遊戲中的公司Guiding Hand Social Club（GHSC）曾經透過其目標CEO的信任在虛擬空間中「暗殺」了這名CEO，隨後竊取價值數十億ISK的財產<ref name="GHSCAssassination">{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=180867&site=pcg |title=Murder Incorporated |accessdate=2008-07-12 |last=Francis |first=Tom |date=2008-02-29 |publisher=PC Gamer |archive-date=2008-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080131073037/http://computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=180867&site=pcg |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這個詐騙案在遊戲中與媒體間皆引起了關注。<ref name="SoftpediaNewsEIBScam">{{cite web |url=http://news.softpedia.com/news/Eve-Online-Economy-Suffers-700-billion-ISK-Scam-33737.shtml |title=Eve Online Economy Suffers 700 billion ISK Scam |accessdate=2007-07-03 |last=Stefanescu |first=Tudor |date=2007-08-24 |publisher=Softpedia |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307062653/http://news.softpedia.com/news/Eve-Online-Economy-Suffers-700-billion-ISK-Scam-33737.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而遊戲開發者表示他們並不負責處理《EVE Online》中的虛擬經濟及瑣事。<ref name="faq67spy">{{cite web |url=http://www.eve-online.com/faq/faq_06.asp |title=Frequently Asked Questions, section 6.7: Can I be a corporate spy? |accessdate=2007-11-08 |author=CCP Games |publisher=CCP Games |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071026113409/http://www.eve-online.com/faq/faq_06.asp |archive-date=2007-10-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>如同真實世界，玩家在遊戲中必須透過自我判斷進行理財與投資。

=== 開發人員作弊 ===
2007年2月9日，一名稱為Kugutsumen的玩家揭露《EVE Online》開發者t20提供他在遊戲中的聯盟──Band of Brothers（BOB）十張昂貴的藍圖，讓BOB在與其他聯盟競爭時具有優勢。<ref name="escapistjumpgate">{{cite web |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/editorials/op-ed/847-Jumpgate-EVE-s-Devs-and-the-Friends-They-Keep |title=Article "Jumpgate: EVE's Devs and the Friends They Keep" |accessdate=2007-12-04 |first=Joe |last=Blancato |date=2007-02-09 |publisher=The Escapist |language=en |archive-date=2008-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080607103137/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/editorials/op-ed/847-Jumpgate-EVE-s-Devs-and-the-Friends-They-Keep |dead-url=no }}</ref>最終t20仍然保留其開發者的地位，而Kugutsumen則因其違反服務條款（Terms of Service）與使用者授權合約而被永久封鎖<ref name="escapistjumpgate" />。作為此事件的回應，CCP派其內部事務部門的領導者Ari Eldon（CCP Arkanon）負責監視遊戲開發者的帳號操作，然而其公平性仍具爭議。<ref name="devblog429">{{cite web |url=http://myeve.eve-online.com/devblog.asp?a=blog&bid=429 |title=Blog post "CCP's director of internal affairs: an introduction" |accessdate=2007-12-04 |author=CCP Arkanon |date=2007-02-13 |publisher=CCP Games |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071120111038/http://myeve.eve-online.com/devblog.asp?a=blog&bid=429 |archive-date=2007-11-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="New York Times">{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/07/arts/07eve.html |title=Article "In a Virtual Universe, the Politics Turn Real" |accessdate=2008-01-26 |first=Seth |last=Schiesel |date=2007-06-07 |publisher=紐約時報 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112042412/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/07/arts/07eve.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 星際議會 ===
為了解決上述的問題，CCP在2008年3月決定選擇9名玩家作為星際議會（Council of Stellar Management，CSM）的代表人以監督開發人員的行為，一共有66人參選<ref name="dev_blog_csm_timeline_xhagen">{{cite web |url=http://myeve.eve-online.com/devblog.asp?a=blog&bid=545 |title=Dev blog "The Council of Stellar Management" |accessdate=2008-06-15 |author=CCP Xhagen |date=2008-03-18 |publisher=CCP Games |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706004344/http://myeve.eve-online.com/devblog.asp?a=blog&bid=545 |archive-date=2008-07-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="csm_overview_pdf">{{cite web |url=http://myeve.eve-online.com/download/devblog/CSMSummary.pdf |title=The CSM - A Summary Explanation of the Council of Stellar Management |accessdate=2008-06-15 |first=Pétur Jóhannes |last=Óskarsson |date=2008-04-18 |format=PDF |publisher=CCP Games |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117171637/http://myeve.eve-online.com/download/devblog/CSMSummary.pdf |archive-date=2009-01-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="dev_blog_csm_results_xhagen">{{cite web |url=http://myeve.eve-online.com/devblog.asp?a=blog&bid=562 |title=Dev blog "Council of Stellar Management: The Results Are in!" |accessdate=2008-06-15 |author=CCP Xhagen |date=2008-05-21 |publisher=CCP Games |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080618073304/http://myeve.eve-online.com/devblog.asp?a=blog&bid=562 |archive-date=2008-06-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，所有候選人必須告知CCP真實姓名與其它遊戲人物的細節。<ref name="forum_post_xhagen_csm_real_names">{{cite web |url=http://myeve.eve-online.com/ingameboard.asp?a=topic&threadID=729021&page=3#78 |title=Eve Online forum topic "The Council of Stellar Management, new blog by Xhagen" |accessdate=2008-06-15 |author=CCP Xhagen |date=2008-03-19 |publisher=CCP Games |language=en }}{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>經過了兩個星期的投票後，第一批代表人選出，包含七名男性與兩名女性，其中各三名來自[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]與[[英國|英國]]，兩名來自[[美國|美國]]及一名來自[[丹麥|丹麥]]，年紀介於17歲與52歲之間<ref name="dev_blog_csm_results_xhagen" />，每個代理人的任期為六個月，且每個人僅能擔任兩次代表人。<ref name="csm_overview_pdf" />

然而，星際議會的本質已經被改變，現被視為玩家向CCP提出請求與改善的主要渠道。<ref name="csm_overview_pdf" />

2008年6月19日至6月23日，星際議會的成員與CCP及其它開發者、遊戲管理員、設計師與媒體在冰島首都[[雷克雅維克|雷克雅維克]]會面<ref name="NYT_on_CSM">{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/28/arts/television/28eve.html?ref=arts |title=Face to Face: A Council of online gamers |accessdate=2008-06-28 |first=Seth |last=Schiesel |date=2008-06-28 |publisher=紐約時報 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308164549/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/28/arts/television/28eve.html?ref=arts |dead-url=no }}</ref>，當時研討玩家所提出的意見，部分意見因技術上的問題而拒絕，但大多數的意見皆被CCP接受，作為未來的發展計畫之一。
===营运史最大规模战争===
在[[太平洋时间|当地时间]]2014年1月29日在宁静服（Tranquility）上，由于一个联盟忘记支付一个空间站的占用费，导致另外两个联盟和其他联盟乘虚而入争抢该空间站而爆发了大型战争，为游戏十年营运史最大规模的一次战争，有7500名玩家参与，导致了包括泰坦——该游戏最大级别的战舰，花费数月建造，约合每艘3000美元——损失75艘，共11万亿游戏货币的损失，约合30~33万美元，并引起[[美联社|美联社]]的关注，运营商也多次为服务器减低负载。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.buffalonews.com/associated-press/2014-14-01/eve-online-epic-game-battle-ends-after-21-hours|title='EVE Online' epic game battle ends after 21 hours - Associated Press - The Buffalo News|access-date=2014-02-04|archive-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113060802/http://www.buffalonews.com/associated-press/2014-14-01/eve-online-epic-game-battle-ends-after-21-hours|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://games.ifeng.com/yejiehangqing/detail_2014_01/30/33501138_0.shtml|title=EVE大战损失28万美元 已惊动美联社战地记者{{!}}EVE{{!}}战斗记者_凤凰游戏|access-date=2014-02-04|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808115102/http://games.ifeng.com/yejiehangqing/detail_2014_01/30/33501138_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

之后[[北京时间|北京时间]]2014年3月25日，晨曦服（Serenity）也爆发了更大规模的一次会战，导致了服务器两次停机维护，和引起国外游戏玩家关注并通过[[twitch|twitch]]直播观看。根据官方的统计截止28日，仅旗舰级裸船破坏造成的游戏内货币损失就以超过29万亿游戏货币，其中泰坦84艘以上，以淘宝上的交易价格换算，约为人民币43.5万元——这还没算上普通舰船和价值更大的船支装备的损失。有人认为这是多个联盟的竞争激化和对之前宁静服大会战的响应。<ref>{{cite web|title=EVE国服爆发史上最激烈会战 超过百艘泰坦被毁_网易游戏|url=http://game.163.com/14/0328/16/9OEHFOKO00314J6L.html|access-date=2014-08-27|archive-date=2015-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219075028/http://game.163.com/14/0328/16/9OEHFOKO00314J6L.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=单日损失超过去8年之和！《EVE》昨日爆发决战 _网络游戏新闻_17173.com中国游戏第一门户站|url=http://news.17173.com/content/2014-03-26/20140326111723217_2.shtml|access-date=2014-08-27|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807113137/http://news.17173.com/content/2014-03-26/20140326111723217_2.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 付费模式 ==
《EVE Online》起初的付费制版本设有试玩期，玩家在超过试玩期限后将无法登录游戏，在Ascension资料片推出后，EVE的付费模式则分为两种账户状态，即免费用户阿尔法（α）与付费用户欧米伽（Ω），两者不设游戏期限，但阿尔法账户的舰船驾驶、技能训练等功能受到一定限制，而欧米伽账户则可自由体验所有游戏内容。

